Pendulum Effect
 You cannot Pendulum Summon monsters, except "Shaddoll" or "Sephira" monsters. This effect cannot be negated.

 Monster Effect
 If this card is Pendulum Summoned, or if this card is sent to the Graveyard: You can target 1 "Sephira" card in your Pendulum Zones, except "Ore-Shaddoll Sephira Roots"; Special Summon it. You can only use this effect of "Ore-Shaddoll Sephira Roots" once per turn.
